UNICEF-Vision
=========


Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install unicef-vision


Setup
-----

Add ``unicef_vision`` to ``INSTALLED_APPS`` in settings

.. code-block:: bash

    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        ...
        'unicef_vision',
    ]


